    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Made with passion by a one man dev team:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352120/extras/3b0cdcce95c3df8ca4ebcb0bb3e0fb88.avif?t=1728484877\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352120/extras_big/3b0cdcce95c3df8ca4ebcb0bb3e0fb88.avif?t=1728484877 width=800 height=781 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is the demo to Hellbreach: Vegas, </strong> a wave-based demon shooter, made by Ash, the one-man army behind Infinity Ape Studios. Play as a solo survivor or a team of up to four and face a demonic threat. Set new records as you shoot your way through waves of demons in the neon-lit streets of Las Vegas. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352120/extras/7cfec88ee69f775dbaac89a740c9e9d1.avif?t=1728484877\" width=616 height=172 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The demo has 1 game mode: Survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1 map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 18 guns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 melee weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 11 perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 slot machines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 9 enemy types</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The <strong>full game</strong> has 4 game modes: Survive, Trapped, Gun Pro, and Royale</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 7 maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 18 guns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 melee weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 11 perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 slot machines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 9 enemy types</p></li></ul>",
